{% comment %}
  FAQ / Help accordion section.

  Each block is a question + answer "drawer" built on a native <details> element:
  click the question to expand the answer, which pushes the following items down.

  Brand styling (skin-car):
  - Collapsed question rectangle uses the dark-navy brand colour.
  - On hover the rectangle turns the light brand blue.
  - The drawers force the `.color-scheme-1` palette (brand navy bg / off-white text /
    light-blue primary) so the look is consistent regardless of the section's own
    background scheme. The section background uses the merchant-chosen colour scheme.
{% endcomment %}

{% style %}
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} {
    margin-top: {{ section.settings.margin_top }}rem;
    margin-bottom: {{ section.settings.margin_bottom }}rem;
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="faq color-{{ section.settings.color_scheme }}">
  {%- if section.settings.heading != blank or section.settings.subheading != blank -%}
    <div class="faq__header">
      {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
        <h2 class="faq__heading">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
      {%- endif -%}
      {%- if section.settings.subheading != blank -%}
        <p class="faq__subheading">{{ section.settings.subheading }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- if section.blocks.size > 0 -%}
    <div class="faq__inner">
      <div class="faq__list">
        {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
          <details
            class="faq__item color-scheme-1"
            {% if block.settings.open_by_default %}open{% endif %}
            {{ block.shopify_attributes }}
          >
            <summary class="faq__question">
              <span class="faq__question-text">{{ block.settings.question }}</span>
              <span class="faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg
                  class="faq__icon-svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  width="22"
                  height="22"
                  fill="none"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  focusable="false"
                >
                  <path
                    d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                  />
                </svg>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="faq__answer">
              <div class="faq__answer-inner rte">{{ block.settings.answer }}</div>
            </div>
          </details>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}
</div>

{% stylesheet %}
  .faq {
    background-color: var(--color-background);
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    padding-inline: var(--page-margin);
    padding-block: 4.5rem;
  }

  .faq__inner {
    max-width: 52rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  /* Heading sits flush to the page margin at full page width — left-aligned
     like the catalog/collection header, not aligned with the card column. */
  .faq__header {
    max-width: var(--page-width);
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .faq__heading {
    text-align: left;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .faq__subheading {
    text-align: left;
    color: var(--color-foreground-muted, var(--color-foreground));
    margin: 0.75rem 0 0;
    max-width: 40rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .faq__list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    /* Allow height keyword (auto) to be animated when a drawer opens. */
    interpolate-size: allow-keywords;
  }

  .faq__item {
    background-color: var(--color-background);
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 0;
    transition: background-color var(--animation-speed, 0.2s) var(--animation-easing, ease);
  }

  /* Question rectangle (the clickable summary). */
  .faq__question {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding: 1.15rem 1.35rem;
    margin: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    background-color: transparent;
    transition: background-color var(--animation-speed, 0.2s) var(--animation-easing, ease),
      color var(--animation-speed, 0.2s) var(--animation-easing, ease);
  }

  .faq__question::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  /* Hover → light brand blue rectangle. */
  .faq__question:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-primary-button-text);
  }

  .faq__question:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    outline-offset: -2px;
  }

  /* Open → the whole card (question + answer) turns the light brand blue. */
  .faq__item[open] {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-primary-button-text);
  }

  .faq__item[open] .faq__question,
  .faq__item[open] .faq__answer-inner {
    color: var(--color-primary-button-text);
  }

  .faq__question-text {
    flex: 1 1 auto;
  }

  /* Down-chevron icon, flips to an up-chevron when the drawer is open. */
  .faq__icon {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: transform var(--animation-speed, 0.25s) var(--animation-easing, ease);
  }

  .faq__item[open] .faq__icon {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  /* Answer reveal — native <details> pushes following items down; the
     ::details-content animation makes that expansion smooth. */
  .faq__answer {
    overflow: hidden;
    /* Divider between the question and the answer (only visible when open). */
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary-button-text) 30%, transparent);
  }

  .faq__item::details-content {
    block-size: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    opacity: 0;
    interpolate-size: allow-keywords;
    transition: content-visibility var(--animation-speed, 0.3s) allow-discrete,
      opacity var(--animation-speed, 0.3s) var(--animation-easing, ease),
      block-size var(--animation-speed, 0.3s) var(--animation-easing, ease);
  }

  /* Don't animate opens that aren't a direct user interaction (e.g. an
     "open by default" drawer expanding on page load). */
  .faq__item:not(:focus-within)::details-content {
    transition: none;
  }

  .faq__item[open]::details-content {
    block-size: auto;
    opacity: 1;

    @starting-style {
      block-size: 0;
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }

  .faq__answer-inner {
    padding: 1.35rem 1.35rem 1.35rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
  }

  .faq__answer-inner > :first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .faq__answer-inner > :last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .faq__answer-inner a {
    color: var(--color-primary-button-text);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .faq {
      padding-block: 3rem;
    }

    .faq__question {
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .faq__item,
    .faq__question,
    .faq__icon,
    .faq__item::details-content {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "FAQ",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "margin_top",
      "label": "Top margin",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 10,
      "step": 0.5,
      "unit": "rem",
      "default": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "margin_bottom",
      "label": "Bottom margin",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 10,
      "step": 0.5,
      "unit": "rem",
      "default": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "color_scheme",
      "id": "color_scheme",
      "label": "Color scheme",
      "default": "scheme-2"
    },
    {
      "type": "inline_richtext",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "Perguntas Frequentes"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "subheading",
      "label": "Subheading",
      "default": "Tudo o que precisas de saber sobre o cuidado do teu carro."
    }
  ],
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "faq_item",
      "name": "Question",
      "settings": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "question",
          "label": "Question",
          "default": "A tua pergunta aqui?"
        },
        {
          "type": "richtext",
          "id": "answer",
          "label": "Answer",
          "default": "<p>Escreve aqui a resposta para ajudar os teus clientes.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "checkbox",
          "id": "open_by_default",
          "label": "Open by default",
          "default": false
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "FAQ",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Como devo lavar o meu carro sem riscar a pintura?",
            "answer": "<p>Usa o método dos dois baldes (um com champô, outro só com água para enxaguar a luva), uma luva de microfibra de qualidade e lava sempre de cima para baixo. Seca com uma toalha de microfibra macia em vez de deixar secar ao ar.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Com que frequência devo aplicar cera ou selante?",
            "answer": "<p>Para a maioria dos carros, recomendamos reaplicar a cada 2 a 3 meses. Se usares um selante ou revestimento cerâmico, a proteção dura bastante mais — podes esticar até 6 meses ou mais, dependendo da exposição ao sol e da lavagem.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Os vossos produtos são seguros para qualquer tipo de pintura?",
            "answer": "<p>Sim. Todos os nossos produtos têm pH equilibrado e são seguros para pinturas com verniz, mate e revestimentos cerâmicos. Em caso de dúvida, testa sempre primeiro numa zona pouco visível.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Quanto tempo demora a entrega?",
            "answer": "<p>As encomendas são processadas em 24 a 48 horas úteis. Depois disso, a entrega em Portugal Continental demora normalmente 1 a 3 dias úteis. Recebes sempre um código de seguimento por email.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Posso devolver um produto se não ficar satisfeito?",
            "answer": "<p>Claro. Tens 14 dias após a receção para devolver qualquer produto não utilizado. Basta entrares em contacto connosco e tratamos de tudo contigo.</p>"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
